將在頒布後五年失效。"},{"pid":"a40bcbaee0eabe534a10818a2020e00943c91cc1","tid":2087820,"uid":26591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:06:04.000Z","msg":"快啲取消<br />\n<br />\n取消埋啲高官嘅外國國籍<br />\n<br />\n堅決反對外國勢力對港進行分裂行為<br />\n<br />\n擁護香港一國一制<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d1dad1a4c6b63f602140507b39129deed8231f","tid":2087820,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7347e0591a2dae177ba4d4996d969a0223852520","tid":2087820,"uid":163841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aeef6ba4e04152573334293c809e2921e3fe2ef","tid":2087820,"uid":183758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f9c33086015b19f0ff3ca286c642946aa522e95","tid":2087820,"uid":163841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:57:11.000Z","msg":"去邊度都要簽證，仲收到貴一貴仲要未必批准<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:59:47.000Z","msg":"唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:03:08.000Z","msg":"有BNO唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626fb99c9aec3c0d101ad4586258c1e52d29f01a","tid":2087820,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa526414418fe5d956755d21c46945e97b4a7b4a","tid":2087820,"uid":273294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:04:49.000Z","msg":"新鮮熱辣：盧比奧提議「香港安全港法」庇護港人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rubio.senate.gov/public/index.cfm/press-releases?ID=3DF99C68-A483-4B35-B6CA-7C9F53845C4B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2